markdownRemark.html:
What Can I Do?

A lot of new developers feel that they don’t have much to offer to the community. This is completely not true. Take time to blog, attend meetups, and give back by helping others that are just getting started. Honestly, in some ways you have more to offer a beginner than someone with 20 years experience.

frontmatter.title: I Don't Have Enough Experience
frontmatter.description: I don't have much experience therefore I don't have anything people want to hear
